input: what is the minimum total cost of a hospital, including a procedure called bronchodilator - leukotriene
predict:
SELECT 
    p.hospitalid, 
    SUM(c.cost) AS total_cost
FROM 
    patient p
JOIN 
    medication m ON p.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
JOIN 
    cost c ON p.uniquepid = c.uniquepid 
            AND p.patienthealthsystemstayid = c.patienthealthsystemstayid 
            AND c.eventtype = 'medication' 
            AND c.eventid = m.medicationid
WHERE 
    LOWER(m.drugname) LIKE '%bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonist%'
GROUP BY 
    p.hospitalid
ORDER BY 
    total_cost ASC
LIMIT 1;
real: select min(t1.c1) from ( select sum(cost.cost) as c1 from cost where cost.patienthealthsystemstayid in ( select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid from patient where patient.patientunitstayid in ( select treatment.patientunitstayid from treatment where treatment.treatmentname = 'bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonists' ) ) group by cost.patienthealthsystemstayid ) as t1;
